		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I wonder if someone's using compatibility with ROMs specifically designed to exercise edge cases, as seen in <a href="http://tasvideos.org/EmulatorResources/NESAccuracyTests.html" class="postlink">this chart</a>, as a proxy for &quot;percent accuracy&quot;. I wrote other thoughts on this in <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?p=119495#p119495" class="postlink">another post</a> as well as the <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Accuracy" class="postlink">&quot;Accuracy&quot; article on the wiki</a>.

		

		</td>
